You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
This might come as a shock to you, but you've just walked into a kitchen.

A closed fridge is in the corner. You can see a closed oven close by. Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a table. You see a cookbook on the table. You see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a red hot pepper, a raw red potato and a knife. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. But the thing hasn't got anything on it.

There is a closed frosted-glass door leading south. There is an exit to the north.

On the counter you can make out a red hot pepper, a raw red potato and a knife. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. But the thing hasn't got anything on it.
